00:12:25.000 --> 00:12:27.000 line:13 position:0% align:left size:100% background:black color:white
<i>Jerrica Escoto</i>: who was six years old at the time.

00:12:27.000 --> 00:12:32.000 line:13 position:0% align:left size:100% background:black color:white
<i>Jerrica Escoto</i>: She named me after her favorite cartoon: Jem and the Holograms.

00:12:32.000 --> 00:12:35.000 line:13 position:0% align:left size:100% background:black color:white
<i>Jerrica Escoto</i>: My parents are from Pampanga, Philippines.

00:12:35.000 --> 00:12:42.000 line:13 position:0% align:left size:100% background:black color:white
<i>Jerrica Escoto</i>: I was raised in southeast San Diego two blocks from Skyline Drive, where blues and reds fought skin till it turned black and purple.

00:12:42.000 --> 00:12:49.000 line:13 position:0% align:left size:100% background:black color:white
<i>Jerrica Escoto</i>: I adopted cursing as my primary language, my tongue grew pointy like the stars on the American flag.

00:12:49.000 --> 00:12:57.000 line:13 position:0% align:left size:100% background:black color:white
<i>Jerrica Escoto</i>: It didn't expand like the sun on the flag of the Philippines, until my grandmother was on her deathbed, and I had to say I love you to her in English.

00:12:57.000 --> 00:13:04.000 line:13 position:0% align:left size:100% background:black color:white
<i>Jerrica Escoto</i>: It didn't occur to me that I had spent my whole life okay with the fact that my grandmother never really understood me.

00:13:04.000 --> 00:13:10.000 line:13 position:0% align:left size:100% background:black color:white
<i>Jerrica Escoto</i>: In my middle school, you were either cool with the black kids or the Asian who got picked on, so this was about survival.

00:13:10.000 --> 00:13:13.000 line:13 position:0% align:left size:100% background:black color:white
<i>Jerrica Escoto</i>: I took on a culture that did not match my golden skin,

00:13:13.000 --> 00:13:18.000 line:13 position:0% align:left size:100% background:black color:white
<i>Jerrica Escoto</i>: took pride in being the honorary black friend in the group 'cause our own ethnicity is unappealing.

00:13:18.000 --> 00:13:20.000 line:13 position:0% align:left size:100% background:black color:white
<i>Jerrica Escoto</i>: My ex-girlfriends are predominantly black.

00:13:20.000 --> 00:13:24.000 line:13 position:0% align:left size:100% background:black color:white
How can I be attracted to a face that looks like mine when I loathe what I see in the mirror?

00:13:24.000 --> 00:13:29.000 line:13 position:0% align:left size:100% background:black color:white
<i>Jerrica Escoto</i>: I am Filipino-American and discovering the Filipino part means castaway on this land.

00:13:29.000 --> 00:13:33.000 line:13 position:0% align:left size:100% background:black color:white
<i>Jerrica Escoto</i>: It's hard to find myself in a nation that resembles broken puzzle pieces,

00:13:33.000 --> 00:13:35.000 line:13 position:0% align:left size:100% background:black color:white
<i>Jerrica Escoto</i>: a home that feels more gift shop than museum.

00:13:35.000 --> 00:13:42.000 line:13 position:0% align:left size:100% background:black color:white
<i>Jerrica Escoto</i>: When the only exposure mainstream news has on the Philippines is for Manny Pacquiao or natural disasters.

00:13:42.000 --> 00:13:47.000 line:13 position:0% align:left size:100% background:black color:white
<i>Jerrica Escoto</i>: When the Filipino channel features commercials and game shows mimicking American pop culture,

00:13:47.000 --> 00:13:49.000 line:13 position:0% align:left size:100% background:black color:white
<i>Jerrica Escoto</i>: When Tagalog is becoming tagalong English,

00:13:49.000 --> 00:13:52.000 line:13 position:0% align:left size:100% background:black color:white
<i>Jerrica Escoto</i>: When even though the Spanish over a century ago,

00:13:52.000 --> 00:13:55.000 line:13 position:0% align:left size:100% background:black color:white
<i>Jerrica Escoto</i>: there are still traces of them in our last name.

00:13:55.000 --> 00:13:59.000 line:13 position:0% align:left size:100% background:black color:white
<i>Jerrica Escoto</i>: Our identity is endangered and I feel like I am disappearing. Where is my resolve?

00:13:59.000 --> 00:14:03.000 line:13 position:0% align:left size:100% background:black color:white
<i>Jerrica Escoto</i>: I want to evolve into a person whose roots I shouldn't have to dig for.

00:14:03.000 --> 00:14:09.000 line:13 position:0% align:left size:100% background:black color:white
<i>Jerrica Escoto</i>: Being second generation, doesn't have to mean being American comes first.

00:14:09.000 --> 00:14:10.000 line:13 position:0% align:left size:100% background:black color:white
<i>Jerrica Escoto</i>: To my grandmother:

00:14:10.000 --> 00:14:12.000 line:13 position:0% align:left size:100% background:black color:white
<i>Jerrica Escoto</i>: Kaluguran daka.

00:14:12.000 --> 00:14:14.000 line:13 position:0% align:left size:100% background:black color:white
<i>Jerrica Escoto</i>: I love you.

00:14:14.000 --> 00:14:16.000 line:13 position:0% align:left size:100% background:black color:white
<i>Jerrica Escoto</i>: Patawarin mo ako.

00:14:16.000 --> 00:14:17.000 line:13 position:0% align:left size:100% background:black color:white
<i>Jerrica Escoto</i>: Please forgive me.

00:14:17.000 --> 00:14:20.000 line:13 position:0% align:left size:100% background:black color:white
<i>Jerrica Escoto</i>: Ako pa balo no nino ako.

00:14:20.000 --> 00:14:23.000 line:13 position:0% align:left size:100% background:black color:white
<i>Jerrica Escoto</i>: I don't know who I am yet.

00:14:23.000 --> 00:14:25.247 line:13 position:0% align:left size:100% background:black color:white
<i>Jerrica Escoto</i>: I am still searching for the Filipino in me.

00:14:32.000 --> 00:14:36.000 line:13 position:0% align:left size:100% background:black color:white
<i>Regie Cabico</i>: We were the first Filipino family to move into Clinton, Maryland.

00:14:36.000 --> 00:14:40.000 line:13 position:0% align:left size:100% background:black color:white
