00:14:40.000 --> 00:14:45.000 line:13 position:0% align:left size:100% background:black color:white
<i>Regie Cabico</i>: I called our entrance, the little nipa hut on the prairie.

00:14:45.000 --> 00:14:55.000 line:13 position:0% align:left size:100% background:black color:white
