00:14:55.000 --> 00:15:02.000 line:13 position:0% align:left size:100% background:black color:white
<i>Regie Cabico</i>: I have two sisters named Faith and Charity. My name is Regie.

00:15:02.000 --> 00:15:05.000 line:13 position:0% align:left size:100% background:black color:white
<i>Regie Cabico</i>: There is no hope in the family.

00:15:05.000 --> 00:15:07.000 line:13 position:0% align:left size:100% background:black color:white
<i>Regie Cabico</i>: While I was growing up,

00:15:07.000 --> 00:15:14.000 line:13 position:0% align:left size:100% background:black color:white
