00:15:17.000 --> 00:15:23.000 line:13 position:0% align:left size:100% background:black color:white
<i>Regie Cabico</i>: See, my mom gave me piano lessons, 'cause like for Filipinos, it was old fashion karaoke.

00:15:23.000 --> 00:15:26.000 line:13 position:0% align:left size:100% background:black color:white
<i>Regie Cabico</i>: A big hit was memory from Cats.

00:15:26.000 --> 00:15:33.000 line:13 position:0% align:left size:100% background:black color:white
